44.000Z","msg":"鐘意個女仔是沒有所謂的"},{"pid":"01e7af9a8f54f52644f68505cda2b274c39b046e","tid":333351,"uid":50610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以自己有時都有濕疹出，覺得濕疹位好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後會戒口一排又好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但怕復發睇左中醫，食左半年中藥，依家都未試過出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n絲打你有冇諗住睇下醫生？</blockquote><br />\n我都無濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係有朋友有嚴重濕疹<br />\n想睇下巴打點睇咁既女仔<br />\n因爲好多男仔嫌棄</blockquote><br />\n我自己同身邊有個女仔fd之前都有濕疹<br />\n我自己會好在意人地有濕疹啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當自己都有𠴱陣，個fd就話一齊去睇中醫，結果我地兩個都好番，我相信濕疹有得醫<br />\n咁當有濕疹又唔理，咁同肥婆唔減肥個情況差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb33265afe5400c596b2e0db3941e94c262c0d21","tid":333351,"uid":27210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無見過真係<span style=\"color: red;\">正常樣好男仔</span>接受到？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇女仔有嚴重濕疹？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評=<span style=\"color: red;\">愛唔會計外表咁膚淺</span><br />\n負評=皮膚唔好慘過肥</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4d23f4ef3b7a393fda76317430fda91cb760c8","tid":333351,"uid":5684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:34:27.000Z","msg":"小弟乽有皮膚病 好明白鐘意人 未一齊已經亂諗野果陣感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454601a2dca7374e7894710d750440d6adcb3f0c","tid":333351,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以自己有時都有濕疹出，覺得濕疹位好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad